<subsection><title>Wrap-Up</title>
<p>In this Lesson, we worked on the following skills and goals related to functions:</p>
<p><ul>
<li><p>Recognize direct variation from a table of values or a graph</p></li>
<li><p>Find the constant of variation and write an equation for the function</p></li> 
<li><p>Sketch the graph of a direct variation </p></li>
</ul></p>

